%202021%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224493%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22432%20Park%20Avenue%20in%20New%20York%20City%20under%20construction%20in%202013.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68169ec23fe8d3928364e077%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222904%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E432%20Park%20Avenue%20in%20New%20York%20City%20was%20under%20construction%20in%202013.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FMark%20Lennihan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20promised%20as%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20condominiums%20in%20the%20City%20was%20instead%20delivered%20riddled%20with%20over%201%2C500%20identified%20construction%20and%20design%20defects%20to%20the%20common%20elements%20of%20the%20Building%20alone%20(leaving%20aside%20the%20numerous%20defects%20within%20individual%20units)%2C%26quot%3B%20tenants%20said%20in%20the%202021%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecomplaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20the%20developers%20%26quot%3Brefused%20to%20accept%20responsibility%20for%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20its%20errors%26quot%3B%20and%20didn't%20properly%20address%20the%20defects.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20building's%20developers%20defended%20themselves%20in%20a%202021%20court%20filing%3A%20%26quot%3B432%20Park%20had%20such%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20no%20different%20from%20any%20other%20building.%20Plaintiffs%2C%20however%2C%20have%20vastly%20exaggerated%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20work%20that%20was%20required%20(both%20in%20the%20reports%20of%20their%20consultant%2C%20SBI%20Consultants%2C%20Inc.%20(%26quot%3BSBI%26quot%3B)%2C%20and%20in%20their%20Complaint)%20in%20furtherance%20of%20their%20gambit%20to%20exact%20undue%20payments%20from%20Sponsor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20the%20tenants%20filed%20a%20second%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20group%2C%20as%20well%20as%20service%20firm%20WSP%2C%20SLCE%20Architects%2C%20and%20McGraw%20Hudson%20Construction%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20founder%20of%20Macklowe%20Properties.%20The%20unit%20owners%20said%20those%20companies%20knew%20%26quot%3Bsince%20the%20outset%20of%20construction%20that%20the%20Building's%20white%20concrete%20fa%C3%A7ade's%20design%20was%20wholly%20defective%20and%20would%20never%20hold%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20developers%20%26quot%3Bconspired%20with%20the%20other%20Defendants%20to%20concoct%20and%20disseminate%20fraudulent%20misrepresentations%20through%20the%20condominium%20offering%20plan%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Buildings%20to%20conceal%20these%20alarming%20defects%20from%20Unit%20Owners%20in%20order%20to%20secure%20massive%20profits%20and%20leave%20Plaintiffs%20holding%20the%20bag%2C%26quot%3B%20unit%20owners%20said%20in%20the%20April%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227086%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20432%20Park%20Avenue%2C%20a%20luxury%20condominium%2C%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68152343c6ad288d147fe8cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20group%20representing%20unit%20owners%20has%20sued%20the%20building's%20developers.%3Cp%3EVictor%20LOCHON%2FGamma-Rapho%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202024%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20published%20an%20analysis%20from%20real-estate%20listings%20and%20property%20records%2C%20as%20well%20as%20interviews%20with%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20building%2C%20that%20showed%20that%20the%20ongoing%20issues%20and%20legal%20action%20have%20pushed%20down%20sales%20activity%20and%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompass%20realtors%20Alexandra%20Hedaya%20and%20Jason%20Haber%2C%20however%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they%20hadn't%20yet%20seen%20any%20impact%20on%20prices%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20hold%20the%20listing%20for%20a%204%2C462-square-foot%2C%20five-bedroom%20on%20the%2055th%20floor%20now%20listed%20for