t%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f966f0c6ad288d147dfa46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222303%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGalleon%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Amanda%20Orson.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Amanda%20Orson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20Craigslist%2C%20but%20for%20homes%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20idea%20behind%20Galleon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGalleon%20is%20an%20off-market%2C%20for-sale-by-owner%20residential%20marketplace%20that%20lets%20homeowners%20name%20their%20prices%20to%20see%20if%20any%20buyers%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20there%20should%20be%20a%20free%20and%20open%20consumer-led%20marketplace%2C%26quot%3B%20Amanda%20Orson%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20Galleon%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20similar%20to%20platforms%20like%20Zillow%20and%20Redfin%2C%20Galleon%20removes%20brokers%20and%20agents%20entirely%20%E2%80%94%20a%20move%20the%20company%20said%20can%20save%20sellers%20%2430%2C000%20or%20more%2C%20presuming%20a%20typical%206%25%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGalleon%20doesn't%20post%20days-on-the-market%20data%20for%20its%20listings%2C%20which%20Orson%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20gives%20sellers%20%26quot%3Bno%20incentive%20not%20to%20try%26quot%3B%20going%20without%20a%20broker.%20On%20traditional%20platforms%2C%20a%20high%20days-on-the-market%20figure%20on%20a%20listing%20might%20lead%20prospective%20buyers%20to%20think%20a%20property%20is%20either%20priced%20too%20high%20or%20that%20something%20is%20wrong%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreating%20a%20listing%20on%20Galleon's%20app%20or%20website%20is%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20%24299%2C%20sellers%20can%20upgrade%20their%20listings%20with%20professional%20photography%2C%20a%20digital%20yard%20sign%20with%20a%20QR%20code%20so%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esellers%20don't%20have%20to%20post%20their%20phone%20numbers%20publicly%2C%20and%20featured%20placement%20on%20Galleon's%20website%20for%20added%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20wanting%20more%20support%2C%20Galleon's%20%24899%20package%20includes%20tools%20like%20a%20scheduling%20calendar%20for%20inspections%20and%20appraisals%2C%20an%20offer%20management%20dashboard%2C%20in-app%20e-signing%2C%20and%20access%20to%20legal%20support%20%E2%80%94%20all%20aimed%20at%20simplifying%20the%20sales%20process%20and%20cutting%20down%20out-of-pocket%20costs%20for%20the%20seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20think%20there%20is%20a%20future%20without%20agents%2C%26quot%3B%20Orson%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20that%20there%20is%20a%20minority%20of%20people%20who%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20transact%20without%20one.%20That's%20who%20we're%20here%20to%20support.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20is%20free%20for%20home%20buyers%20and%20available%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EListwise%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223584%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20headshot%20of%20Nic%20Johnson%2C%20founder%20of%20ListWise.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ffc892c6ad288d147e4bdb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EListWise%20founder%20Nic%20Johnson.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Nic%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EListwise%20isn't%20trying%20to%20push%20real%20estate%20agents%20out%20of%20the%20picture%20%E2%80%94%20its%20aim%20is%20to%20help%20home%20sellers%20find%20the%20right%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%2C%20aimed%20primarily%20at%20sellers%2C%20uses%20an%20incentive-based%20commission%20model%20designed%20to%20boost%20competition%20between%20agents%20and%20improve%20transparency%20for%20home%20sellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20works%3A%20On%20Listwise's%20digital%20platform%2C%20sellers%20share%20the%20commission%20amount%20they're%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20listing%20agent%20and%20what%20they're%20looking%20for%20in%20one%20%E2%80%94%20including%20number%20of%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20importance%20of%20local%20market%20knowledge%2C%20or%20whether%20they%20prefer%20someone%20from%20a%20big-name%20brokerage%20or%20a%20smaller%20local%20firm.%20Sellers%20also%20propose%20how%20much%20they%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20the%20buyers'%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EListwise%20then%20matches%20the%20sellers%20with%20qualified%20listing%20agents%20in%20its%20network%20who%20meet%20those%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20listing%20agent%20then%20bids%20for%20the%20listing%20by%20submitting%20a%20personalized%20offer%20that%20includes%20their%20commission%20charge.%20If%20a%20seller%20chooses%20one%20of%20those%20agents%20and%20the%20home%20sells%2C%20that%20agent%20pays%20Listwise%20a%20referral%20fee%20or%20commission%20for%20helping%20them%20win%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOff-Markt%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alison%20Bernstein%20poses%20in%20an%20all-white%20outfit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f96215c6ad288d147df8e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221146%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOff-Markt%20founder%20Alison%20Bernstein.%3Cp%3EOlivia%20Steuer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlison%20Bernstein%20first%20got%20the%20idea%20for%20a%20real%20estate%20app%20when%20a%20friend%20sent%20her%20a%20fitness%20influencer's%20Instagram%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBernstein%20liked%20the%20flow%20of%20the%20influencer's%20apartment%20and%20messaged%20her%20directly%20to%20see%20if%20she'd%20be%20interested%20in%20selling.%20They%20ended%20up%20closing%20an%20off-market%20deal.%20Bernstein%20then%20found%20an%20off-market%20buyer%20for%20her%20own%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20inspired%20her%20to%20create%20an%20Off-Markt%2C%20an%20app%20with%20an%20Instagram-like%20interface%20that%20lets%20homeowners%20show%20off%20their%20spaces%20and%20attract%20prospective%20buyers%20year-round%20%E2%80%94%20without%20ever%20formally%20listing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20consumer%20should%20own%20the%20story%20of%20their%20home.%20They%20should%20own%20that%20digital%20footprint%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernstein%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Off-Markt%2C%20a%20user%20creates%20profiles%20for%20their%20home.%20They%20can%20post%20photos%20showing%20off%20the%20best%20features%20of%20their%20property.%20Bernstein's%20hope%20is%20that%20homeowners%20feel%20like%20they%20can%20%26quot%3Bown%20the%20narrative%26quot%3B%20of%20their%20space%20and%20better%20attract%20future%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20average%20consumer%20is%20very%20savvy%2C%26quot%3B%20Bernstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReal%20estate%20agents%20create%20a%20profile%20on%20the%20app%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20%2450%20a%20month%20and%20offer%20their%20services%20to%20users%20who%20might%20need%20extra%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOff-Markt%20declined%20to%20share%20how%20many%20homes%20and%20cities%20are%20currently%20listed%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERedy%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Josh%20Altman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fa49f3c1df1d5001821933e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221654%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERedy%20founder%20Josh%20Altman.%3Cp%3EJosh%20Altman%2FAmy%20Lee%2FPriyanka%20Banerjee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJosh%20Altman%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20agent%20featured%20on%20%26quot%3BMillion%20Dollar%20Listing%20Los%20Angeles%2C%26quot%3B%20cofounded%20Redy%20in%202020%20to%20encourage%20transparent%20competition%20among%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Redy%2C%20agents%20compete%20for%20the%20opportunity%20to%20sell%20your%20home%20by%20offering%20incentives%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Bcash%20bonus%26quot%3B%20and%20competitive%20commission%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20sellers%20get%20paid%20cash%20to%20pick%20an%20agent%3B%20as%20a%20result%2C%20agents%20are%20directly%20invested%20in%20the%20sale%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said%20in%20a%202024%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BAll%20agents%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20own%20local%20seller%20listings%2C%20which%20will%2C%20in%20return%2C%20help%20them%20own%20the%20local%20market%20they%20operate%20in%20and%20level%20the%20playing%20field%20for%20listings.%20When%20you%20own%20local%20seller%20listings%2C%20you%20own%20your%20local%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKenneth%20Bloom%2C%20who%20used%20Redy%20to%20sell%20two%20homes%20in%20Michigan%2C%20told%20BI%20in%202024%20that%20he%20appreciated%20having%20agents%20come%20to%20him.%20Otherwise%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20would've%20had%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20legwork%20to%20find%20the%20right%20person%20to%20sell%20his%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20able%20to%20find%20an%20experienced%20agent%20who%20was%20familiar%20with%20his%20area%20and%20could%20get%20his%20homes%20sold%20fast%2C%20which%20was%20a%20priority%20for%20him.%20He%20ended%20up%20finding%20a%20buyer%20for%20one%20of%20the%20homes%20in%20one%20day%20through%20the%20agent%20he%20found%20on%20Redy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloom%20said%20he%20received%20a%20%241%2C200%20cash%20bonus%20for%20the%20first%20house%20he%20sold%20through%20Redy%20and%20%241%2C040%20on%20the%20second.%20He%20estimated%20he%20saved%20nearly%20%2410%2C000%20on%20broker%20commissions%20between%20the%20two%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERidley%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20headshot%20of%20Mike%20Chambers%20in%20a%20white%20t%20shirt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680ff3ef3fe8d39283644c56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERidley%20founder%20Mike%20Chambers.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mike%20Chambers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20tech%20entrepreneur%20Mike%20Chambers%20wanted%20to%20sell%20his%20Boulder%2C%20Colorado%2C%20home%20in%20February%2C%20he%20didn't%20see%20the%20point%20in%20using%20an%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20his%20five-bedroom%2C%20four-bathroom%20home%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bturnkey%20house%20in%20a%20desirable%20neighborhood.%26quot%3B%20He%20wasn't%20sure%20how%20much%20an%20agent%20would%20have%20to%20do%20besides%20uploading%20the%20home's%20photos%20online%20and%20unlocking%20the%20door%20for%20tours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20Chambers%20listed%20the%20home%20himself%20for%20%242.725%20million%20and%20started%20an%20Instagram%20called%20%40realtorshateme%20to%20document%20his%20for-sale-by-owner%20adventure.%20The%20account%2C%20which%20has%20nearly%2018%2C000%20followers%2C%20quickly%20drew%20the%20ire%20of%20local%20Boulder%20agents.%20Chambers%20told%20BI%20he%20saw%20videos%20of%20agents%20on%20social%20media%20saying%20they%20wouldn't%20take%20clients%20to%20his%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChambers%20found%20an%20out-of-state%20buyer%20through%20Instagram%2C%20but%20his%20family%20ultimately%20decided%20to%20pull%20their%20house%20off%20the%20market%20and%20stay%20in%20Colorado.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20opened%20Chambers'%20eyes%20to%20the%20possibilities%20of%20%E2%80%94%20and%20appetite%20for%20%E2%80%94%20a%20broker-less%20way%20to%20sell%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnter%20Ridley%2C%20a%20new%20app%20that's%20set%20to%20launch%20by%20the%20end%20of%20May.%20It%20will%20offer%20homeowners%20a%20suite%20of%20AI%20agents%20who%20can%20help%20people%20who%20want%20to%20list%20their%20property%20for%20sale%20by%20owner%2C%20or%20FSBO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnology%20has%20basically%20made%20almost%20every%20step%20of%20this%20process%20more%20efficient%2C%20and%20there's%20been%20no%20reflection%20in%20the%20price%20or%20in%20the%20costs%20associated%20with%20these%20transactions%20to%20reflect%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Chambers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20agents%20can%20do%20things%20like%20write%20a%20listing%20description%20or%20book%20photographers.%20%3Cspan%3ESellers%20would%20pay%20a%20one-time%20fee%20of%20%24999%20or%20%241%2C999%20to%20add%20an%20on-call%20lawyer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20product%20like%20this%20that%20empowers%20consumers%20to%20take%20control%20of%20this%20process%20and%20save%20lots%20of%20money%20is%20really%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETurbohome%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20front%20of%20a%20geometric%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65689fbb47f9ecb37d88a14e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETurbohome%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Ben%20Bear.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ben%20Bear%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETurbohome%20is%20a%20real-estate%20brokerage%20that%20pays%20agents%20a%20salary%20rather%20than%20a%20more%20typical%20commission-based%20compensation%20and%20gives%20buyers%20the%20option%20to%20pay%20a%20flat%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20healthcare%2C%20they%20have%20a%20salary%2C%20and%20they%20have%20consistent%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Ben%20Bear%2C%20Turbohome's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Ben%20Bear%2C%20said%20of%20his%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20appealing%20for%20people%20who%20just%20like%20working%20with%20clients%20without%20that%20pressure%20of%20knowing%20how%20they're%20going%20to%20pay%20their%20next%20rent%20check%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20paying%20a%20percentage%20commission%2C%20buyers%20pay%20a%20flat%20fee%20to%20the%20Turbohome%20agent%20%E2%80%94%20between%20%245%2C000%20and%20%2410%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20commission%20given%20to%20the%20agent%20is%20then%20credited%20to%20the%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurbohome's%20site%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bcash%20back%20calculator%26quot%3B%20that%20shows%20buyers%20their%20refund%20based%20on%20a%20home's%20price.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20buyer%20would%20be%20refunded%20%2435%2C000%20on%20a%20%241.5%20million%20home%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArnab%20Dutta%20used%20Turbohome%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20in%202024%20after%20trying%20the%20traditional%20route%20without%20success%20in%20years%20past%2C%20and%20his%20offer%20beat%20out%20other%20offers%20because%20he%20said%20the%20seller%20didn't%20have%20to%20pay%20his%20agent's%20commission%2C%20he%20previously%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurbohome%20launched%20in%202024%20and%20had%20raised%20%243.85%20million%20as%20of%20March.%20The%20brokerage%20currently%20operates%20in%20California%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-save-home-sellers-money-on-commissions-avoid-traditional-agents-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746436802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68110b29a466d2b74ab478c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-save-home-sellers-money-on-commissions-avoid-traditional-agents-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Home%20sellers%20have%20some%20options%20beyond%20real%20estate%20agents%20with%20traditional%20commission%20structures%2C%20from%20flat%20fees%20to%20listing%20for%20sale%20by%20owner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dlatu%40insider.com%20(Dan%20Latu%2CJordan%20Pandy%2CAlcynna%20Lloyd)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-save-home-sellers-money-on-commissions-avoid-traditional-agents-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20lists%20PIL%20challenging%20Waqf%20case%20for%20hearing%20on%20May%2015%20by%20next%20CJI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22