3EWe've%20hired%20a%20full-time%20salesperson%20and%20recently%20landed%20the%20Charlotte%20marathon%20as%20a%20client%20by%20quoting%20them%20a%20price%20for%20porta-potty%20rentals.%20They%20told%20us%20no%20competitor%20had%20ever%20reached%20out%20to%20them%20before.%20I%20use%20ChatGPT%20a%20lot%20to%20create%20lists%20of%20the%20top%20fifty%20largest%20outdoor%20events%20in%20Charlotte.%20I%20ask%20it%20to%20provide%20me%20with%20emails%2C%20and%20then%20I%20reach%20out%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20our%20success%20comes%20from%20marketing.%20I%20go%20to%20conventions%2C%20like%20a%20local%20builders%20convention%2C%20and%20hand%20out%20shirts%20that%20say%20%26quot%3BGettin'%20Shit%20Done.%26quot%3B%20None%20of%20our%20competitors%20are%20there%2C%20and%20it's%20super%20memorable.%20At%20Procter%20%26amp%3B%20Gamble%2C%20I%20sold%20products%20to%20large%20chains%20and%20learned%20that%20you%20need%20to%20make%20those%20sales%20pitches%20memorable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d9f8a5c-5902-47d1-b83e-d3d8b4e9eaa8%5C%22%3EThere's%20no%20out%20of%20office%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20weekends%2C%20all%20calls%20are%20routed%20directly%20to%20my%20cellphone.%20A%20few%20weekends%20ago%2C%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20an%20event%20an%20hour%20away%20whose%20toilet%20provider%20hadn't%20shown%20up.%20They%20asked%20for%20my%20help%2C%20so%20I%20threw%20two%20toilets%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20pickup%20truck%20and%20drove%20an%20hour%20both%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20plan%20anything%20on%20Saturday%20until%202%3A00%20p.m.%20because%20there's%20a%2070%25%20chance%20that%20someone%20will%20call%20with%20an%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hardest%20with%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20visiting%20family%20out%20of%20state%20when%20one%20of%20his%20largest%20clients%20called%20to%20say%20that%20they%20had%20an%20emergency%20and%20needed%2010%20portable%20toilets%20delivered%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20If%20I%20were%20nearby%2C%