ng%20what%20you%20think%20you%20should%20be%20creating%2C%20not%20all%20of%20the%20other%20bullshit%20corporate%20America%20hands%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b631389-58d2-4fdc-8c72-4f6a0a587a55%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20no%20'normal'%20days%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20focus%20on%20anything%20but%20work.%20I%20don't%20go%20out%20to%20nice%20dinners%2C%20travel%2C%20or%20hang%20out%20with%20my%20friends%20at%20happy%20hour.%20It's%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20live%20on%20my%20current%20salary%2C%20which%20is%20lower%20than%20my%20corporate%20salary%2C%20because%20I%20don't%20spend%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20sleep%20in%20until%208%3A00%20am%20on%20the%20weekends%20anymore%2C%20or%20easily%20fit%20in%20a%20workout.%20It's%20more%20exciting%2C%20but%20it's%20much%20harder%20to%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bnormal%26quot%3B%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20even%20focus%20on%20food%20or%20exercise.%20I%20had%20a%20wake-up%20call%20after%20I%20put%20on%2015%20pounds%20in%20my%20first%20three%20and%20a%20half%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20in%20Asheville%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20living%20in%20an%20RV%20for%20a%20month%2C%20there%20were%20times%20the%20gas%20station%20was%20my%20only%20option%20for%20a%20full%20meal.%20There%20was%20one%20day%20I%20ate%20Chic-fil-a%20for%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20what%20am%20I%20doing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I'm%20more%20mindful%20about%20what%20I%20eat%2C%20packing%20healthier%20options%20for%20long%20days.%20And%20I%20try%20to%20fit%20in%20a%20workout%20where%20I%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f410c2e0-7246-42cb-b197-8faf589a2006%5C%22%3EYou%20reap%20what%20you%20sow%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOutcomes%20are%20tied%20directly%20to%20my%20effort.%20I'm%20responsible%20for%20the%20business's%20success%2C%20which%20correlates%20to%20how%20hard%20I%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuccess%20in%20corporate%20America%20is%20more%20complicated.%20Promotions%20take%20into%20account%20how%20much%20someone%20likes%20you%2C%20or%20the%20macroeconomic%20environment%2C%20or%20the%20success%20of%20whatever%20product%20comes%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20have%20some%20control%20over%20my%20destiny%2C%20which%20is%20both%20good%20and%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20telling%20example%20was%20how%20I%20responded%20after%20the%20terrible%20hurricane%20in%20Asheville.%20Home%20Depot%20called%20asking%20for%20portable%20toilets%2C%20so%20we%20loaded%20up%20the%20toilets%20and%20drove%20the%20two%20hours%20to%20Asheville.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20our%20toilets%20had%20our%20phone%20number%2C%20and%20the%20next%20day%2C%20I%20had%20222%20voicemails%20while%20still%20fielding%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20shop%20for%20a%20month%20in%20Asheville%2C%20living%20out%20of%20an%20RV%20and%20ordering%20500%20more%20toilets%20to%20meet%20the%20demand.%20By%20choosing%20to%20put%20in%20the%20hard%20work%2C%20I%20set%20my%20business%20up%20for%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290a17e13-6d9c-41f4-b34c-009e92d17302%5C%22%3EBig%20decisions%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20already%20received%20offers%20from%20people%20who%20want%20to%20buy%20the%20business%2C%20but%20I'm%20conflicted%20about%20it.%20I'm%20someone%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20like%20to%20ask%20me%20what%20my%20goal%20is%20for%20the%20company.%20Transparently%2C%20I%20didn't%20really%20have%20an%20end%20goal%20in%20mind.%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20this%20company%20and%20build%20it%20into%20the%20biggest%20portable%20toilet%20company%20in%20Charlotte%2C%20enjoy%20my%20days%2C%20and%20have%20a%20positive%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20sold%20to%20a%20roll-up%20business%2C%20they'd%20still%20want%20me%20to%20run%20it.%20I'd%20have%20equity%20in%20their%20larger%20business%2C%20but%20I%20would%20be%20right%20back%20to%20working%20for%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20wait%20and