son%20Taylor%20Rogers%20cited%20Friday's%20strong%20jobs%20report%20to%20say%20that%20Trump%20was%20bringing%20jobs%20back%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3Eand%20making%20America%20the%20world's%20manufacturing%20powerhouse%20once%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%26quot%3B%20A%20DOE%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20department%20was%20still%20reviewing%20its%20organizational%20structure%20to%20align%20with%20the%20president's%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20American%20people%20provided%20President%20Trump%20with%20a%20mandate%20to%20govern%20and%20to%20unleash%20affordable%2C%20abundant%2C%20and%20secure%20American%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20final%20decisions%20have%20been%20made%20and%20multiple%20plans%20are%20still%20being%20considered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22897da283-7ee5-4134-b3c1-dd5b0c01bc9c%5C%22%3ECanceled%20clean%20energy%20factories%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20job%20fair%20during%20DC's%20inaugural%20Climate%20Week%2C%20more%20than%2050%20companies%20and%20trade%20associations%20met%20some%201%2C200%20job%20seekers.%20They%20lined%20up%20to%20chat%20with%20firms%20including%20Amazon%2C%20the%20solar%20manufacturer%20Qcells%2C%20and%20Arcadia%2C%20an%20AI%20analytics%20platform%20for%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225529%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22More%20than%201%2C200%20people%20attended%20a%20job%20fair%20hosted%20by%20Clean%20Energy%20for%20America%20on%20April%2030.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68152c46c6ad288d147feba5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224042%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMore%20than%201%2C200%20people%20attended%20a%20job%20fair%20hosted%20by%20Clean%20Energy%20for%20America%20on%20April%2030.%3Cp%3EClean%20Energy%20for%20America%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EZainab%20Mirza%20organized%20the%20job%20fair%20for%20Clean%20Energy%20for%20America%2C%20a%20trade%20group%20that%20lobbies%20Congress%20and%20the%20administration%20on%20issues%20like%20protecting%20tax%20credits%20for%20renewable%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMirza%20experienced%20similar%20career%20setbacks%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eas%20Yang.%20She%20graduated%20from%20American%20University%20in%202020%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20which%20thwarted%20her%20plans%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20international%20development%20overseas.%20In%20February%2C%20she%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20the%20DOE's%20Loan%20Program%20Office%2C%20where%20she%20had%20just%20become%20a%20full-time%20employee%20after%20being%20a%20contractor%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20slashed%20investments%20go%20beyond%20the%20federal%20government.%20In%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%202025%2C%20companies%20canceled%2C%20closed%2C%20or%20downsized%20projects%20totaling%20nearly%20%248%20billion%20in%20investment.%20This%20affected%2016%20new%20factories%20for%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20batteries%2C%20and%20hydrogen%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20three%20times%20the%20cancellation%20rate%20over%20the%20previous%2030%20months%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20E2%2C%20a%20business%20group%20that%20advocates%20for%20clean%20energy%2C%20and%20the%20think%20tank%20Atlas%20Public%20Policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20self-inflicted%20and%20unnecessary%20market%20uncertainty%20continues%2C%20we'll%20almost%20certainly%20see%20more%20projects%20paused%2C%20more%20construction%20halted%2C%20and%20more%20job%20opportunities%20disappear%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Timberlake%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20E2%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20January%202024%20and%20March%202025%2C%20the%20number%20of%20new%20job%20postings%20across%20renewable%20power%20%E2%80%94%20including%20solar%2C%20wind%2C%20nuclear%2C%20hydropower%2C%20and%20geothermal%20%E2%80%94%20dropped%20by%20more%20than%2020%25%2C%20indicating%20a%20slowdown%20in%20labor%20demand%2C%20an%20analysis%20Revelio%20Labs%20conducted%20for%20BI%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20companies%20continue%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20energy%20transition.%20In%20March%2C%2010%20solar%2C%20EV%2C%20and%20transmission%20manufacturing%20plants%20were%20announced%2C%20which%2C%20if%20built%2C%20could%20create%205%2C000%20permanent%20jobs.%20That%20includes%20Tesla's%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20battery%20factory%20near%20Houston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdd14342-e006-4da6-9725-0cf0bd512541%5C%22%3EBillions%20of%20dollars%20deployed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20hurdles%2C%20Mirza%20was%20optimistic%20about%20the%20future.%20While%20the%20DOE%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20less%20active%20and%20shift%20away%20from%20wind%20and%20solar%20projects%2C%20it%20may%20help%20finance%20nuclear%2C%20geothermal%2C%20and%20power%20grid%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKatie%20Mehnert%2C%20CEO%20of%20ALLY%20Energy%2C%20an%20online%20career%20and%20networking%20platform%2C%20said%20the%20energy%20industry%20is%20always%20changing.%20Mehnert%20lives%20in%20Texas%2C%20where%20layoffs%20are%20also%20hitting%20the%20oil%20and%20gas%20sector.%20The%20rise%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20is%20ushering%20in%20another%20transformation%20of%20how%20businesses%20operate.%20But%20there%20will%20be%20jobs%2C%20Mehnert%20said.%20ALLY%20recently%20partnered%20with%20Parallell%2C%20an%20AI-driven%20jobs%20platform%20that%20aims%20to%20make%20job%20hunting%20more%20efficient%20and%20better%20match%20people's%20expertise%20to%20openings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20more%20energy%2C%20we%20need%20sustainable%20energy%2C%20we%20need%20affordable%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mehnert%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20there's%20plenty%20of%20money%20that's%20been%20deployed.%20Now%20we%20need%20to%20find%20the%20best%20talent%20and%20match%20them%20with%20opportunities%20quicker.%20That%20way%2C%20we%20can%20minimize%20the%20disruption%20in%20job%20marketing%20and%20people's%20personal%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMirza%2C%20for%20her%20part%2C%20encouraged%20young%20people%20to%20be%20open-minded%20to%20positions%20they%20may%20not%20have%20considered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20where%20I%20want%20to%20go%20next%2C%26quot%3B%20Mirza%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20had%20a%20blast%20putting%20this%20event%20together.%20I%20think%20that%20people%20here%20can%20meet%20with%20employers%20they%20might%20not%20have%20heard%20of%20or%20thought%20about%2C%20or%20a%20skill%20that%20they%20haven't%20developed.%20There%20are%20upskilling%20opportunities.%20There%20are%20incubators.%20Maybe%20you've%20had%20an%20idea%20for%20so%20long%2C%20and%20now%20you%20can%20test%20it%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYang%20said%20he's%20open-minded%2C%20too.%20Although%20his%20time%20at%20DOE%20was%20focused%20on%20long-duration%20energy%20storage%20like%20batteries%2C%20he%20is%20open%20to%20other%20technologies.%20During%20his%20undergrad%20internships%2C%20Yang%20worked%20on%20transmission%20infrastructure%2C%20sales%20teams%2C%20and%20policy%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Yang%20decided%20to%20accelerate%20his%20pursuit%20of%20a%20master's%20in%20energy%2C%20policy%2C%20and%20climate%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University%20while%20looking%20for%20a%20full%20time%20job.%20He's%20come%20close%20several%20times%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20someone%20with%20more%20experience%20was%20hired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20no%20fault%20of%20my%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20Yang%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20ton%20of%20talented%20people%20out%20there%20right%20now%2C%20and%20I%20haven't%20worked%20full-time%20yet.%20So%20I'm%20cautiously%20optimistic.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20my%20future%20holds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acboudreau%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ecboudreau%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zers-clean-energy-climate-job-cuts-doge-trump-musk-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746433021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6814d897c6ad288d147fd472%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zers-clean-energy-climate-job-cuts-doge-trump-musk-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20upheaval%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20has%20clouded%20Gen%20Zs%20career%20paths%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20industry%20as%20Trump%20slashes%20programs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zers-clean-energy-climate-job-cuts-doge-trump-musk-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RIP%20Skype.%20Born%3A%202003.%20Died%3A%20today.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apple%20laptop%20with%20a%20dock%20on%20the%20laptop%20with%20WhatsApp%2C%20Facetime%2C%20Messenger%20and%20Skype%20apps%20with%20the%20delete%20button%20above%20the%20Skype%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68139bf7a466d2b74ab4bc10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENora%20Carol%20Photography%2FGetty%2C%20DrPixel%2FGetty%2C%20Vectorig%2FGetty%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20Facetime%2C%20Messenger%2C%20Skype%2C%20Ava%20Horton%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20were%20wedged%20into%20%26quot%3BBrady%20Bunch%26quot%3B%20squares%20on%20Zoom%20and%20Microsoft%20Teams%2C%20before%20we%20grew%20accustomed%20to%20summoning%20friends%20and%20family%20anytime%2C%20anywhere%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacetime-public-nuisance-speakerphone-epidemic-private-lives-apple-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFaceTime%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20Skype.%20Launched%20in%20Luxembourg%20in%202003%2C%20Skype%20became%20the%20first%20platform%20to%20offer%20free%20computer-to-computer%20voice%20calls%20for%20anyone.%20Soon%20after%2C%20it%20added%20video%20calling%2C%20giving%20birth%20to%20an%20era%20of%20on-demand%20videophoning%20that%20had%20been%20dreamed%20of%20since%20an%20astronaut%20called%20to%20wish%20his%20daughter%20on%20Earth%20a%20happy%20birthday%20in%20%26quot%3B2001%3A%20A%20Space%20Odyssey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Skype%20takes%20its%20final%20resting%20place%20in%20the%20graveyard%20of%20early-2000s%20services%20we%20loved%20and%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20probably%20been%20years%20since%20you've%20made%20a%20call%20over%20Skype%20(though%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dskype%2Bcall%2Bsound%26rlz%3D1C5GCEM_enUS1126US1126%26oq%3Dskype%2Bcall%2Bsound%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyCQgAEEUYORiABDIHCAEQABiABDIHCAIQABiABDIHCAMQABiABDIHCAQQABiABDIHCAUQABiABDIHCAYQABiABDINCAcQABiGAxiABBiKBTIHCAgQABjvBTIHCAkQABjvBdIBCDI3MzdqMGo3qAIAsAIA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%23fpstate%3Dive%26vld%3Dcid%3Ae44b072a%2Cvid%3AtsUyjzRIU9w%2Cst%3A0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edial%20tone%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20still%20lives%20rent-free%20in%20my%20head).%20The%20company%20that%20brought%20us%20a%20miracle%20has%20been%20largely%20pushed%20aside%20and%20cannibalized%20by%20a%20slate%20of%20competitors.%20People%20don't%20care%20much%20about%20which%20video%20platform%20they're%20using%2C%20so%20whatever%20provides%20the%20simplest%20way%20to%20connect%20becomes%20the%20one%20we%20click%20to%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20video%20calling%20built%20into%20our%20phones%2C%20Slack%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20work%20email%2C%20the%20miracle%20has%20turned%20into%20the%20mundane%20%E2%80%94%20even%20a%20nuisance%20at%20times%2C%20when%20we%20need%20to%20go%20camera%20off.%20But%20for%20millennials%2C%20Skype%20was%20the%20magic%20that%20brought%20%26quot%3BThe%20Jetsons%26quot%3B%20to%20life.%20Long-distance%20relationships%20were%20sustained%20on%20laptop%20Skype%20calls%2C%20even%20if%20they%20often%20glitched.%20Getting%20a%20webcam%20became%20a%20monumental%20rite%20of%20passage.%20For%20those%20early%20years%2C%20Skype%20realized%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20darling%20of%20the%20early%20tech%20boom.%20In%202005%2C%20eBay%20bought%20it%20for%20%242.6%20billion%20(a%20time%20when%20Facebook%20was%20worth%20%24100%20million).%20But%20Skype's%20video%20call%20focus%20didn't%20fit%20well%20with%20the%20e-commerce%20giant's%20business%20model.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20eBay%20took%20a%20%241.4%20billion%20write-down%20on%20it%20and%20soon%20after%20began%20divesting%20its%20interests%20in%20Skype.%20A%20private%20equity%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Febay-skype-deal-2009-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etook%20a%20majority%20stake%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202011%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-buying-skype-2011-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMicrosoft%20bought%20Skype%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%248.5%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20its%20largest%20acquisition%20at%20the%20time.%20Some%20170%20million%20people%20were%20making%20Skype%20calls%20monthly%2C%20a%20number%20that%20grew%20to%20300%20million%20by%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20also%20when%20Skype%20started%20to%20lose%20its%20luster.%20%26quot%3BA%20few%20rivals%20started%20to%20emerge%20that%20chipped%20away%20at%20different%20use%20cases%20that%20Skype%20used%20to%20be%20the%20go-to%20tool%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Thomas%20Randall%2C%20an%20advisory%20director%20at%20Info-Tech%20Research%20Group.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-whatsapp-guide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Discord%2C%20and%20Slack%20were%20all%20integrating%20messaging%20and%20video%20calling%2C%20whether%20for%20work%2C%20gaming%2C%20or%20other%20personal%20use.%20Microsoft%20rolled%20out%20Teams%20in%202017.%20Skype's%20mobile%20interface%20lagged%20behind%20what%20became%20its%20internal%20rival%2C%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20brand%20lost%20its%20focus%2C%26quot%3B%20Randall%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202020%2C%20Skype%20saw%20a%20surge%20in%20users%2C%20with%2040%20million%20people%20making%20calls%20daily%2C%20a%2070%25%20increase%20from%20the%20month%20before.%20That%20same%20month%2C%20Microsoft%20announced%20that%20Teams%20would%20roll%20out%20features%20to%20make%20the%20video%20calling%20app%20more%20friendly%20toward%20social%20interactions%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20meantime%2C%20we%20invite%20you%20to%20connect%20with%20friends%20and%20family%20through%20chat%20and%20video%20calling%20using%20Skype.%26quot%3B%20The%20demand%20for%20video%20chatting%2C%20driven%20by%20the%20pandemic%20lockdowns%2C%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20save%20Skype.%20Forty-four%20million%20people%20were%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-teams-coronavirus-daily-active-users-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMicrosoft%20Teams%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20each%20day%20in%20March%202020%2C%20a%20number%20that%20grew%20to%2070%20million%20later%20that%20year.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-zoom-2020-unprecedented-pandemic-growth-executives-new-challenges-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EZoom%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20even%20more%20synonymous%20with%20video%20calling%20and%20grew%20rapidly%20to%20300%20million%20daily%20users%20in%20April%202020.%20As%20of%202023%2C%20only%2036%20million%20people%20were%20still%20hanging%20out%20on%20Skype%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20announced%20in%20February%20that%20it%20would%20sunset%20Skype%20and%20that%20people%20would%20have%20the%20option%20to%20move%20their%20data%20to%20Teams%20or%20export%20it%20by%20May%205.%20%26quot%3BSkype%20has%20been%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20shaping%20modern%20communications%20and%20supporting%20countless%20meaningful%20moments%2C%20and%20we%20are%20honored%20to%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeff%20Teper%2C%20the%20president%20of%20collaborative%20apps%20and%20platforms%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20said%20in%20a%20post%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20a%20Skype%20subreddit%20has%20been%20filled%20with%20the%20app's%20dwindling%20users%2C%20some%20panicking%20as%20they%20try%20to%20find%20a%20replacement%20for%20their%20years-old%20Skype%20numbers%2C%20which%20they%20have%20been%20using%20to%20receive%20authentication%20codes.%20One%20person%20says%20they're%20trying%20to%20switch%20their%20grandma's%20account%20from%20Skype%20to%20Teams%2C%20and%20some%20are%20worried%20about%20training%20older%20relatives%20on%20new%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20are%20watching%20its%20funeral%20with%20delight%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20even%20feel%20sad%20for%20Skype's%20demise%20because%20it's%20been%2014%20years%20of%20shit%20from%20Microsoft%20and%20that's%20what%20I%20remember%20far%20more%20than%20the%208%20years%20before%20the%20buyout%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20wrote%20on%20Reddit.%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20the%20original%20creators%20of%20Skype%20cashed%20out%20big%20time%20and%20are%20enjoying%20a%20nice%20retirement.%20They%20deserve%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Microsoft's%20leadership%2C%20Skype's%20features%20faltered.%20There%20were%20redesigns%20and%20new%20features%2C%20like%20the%20ability%20to%20be%20on%20a%20call%20with%20100%20people%20at%20a%20time%20and%20a%20revamped%20chat%20experience%20on%20mobile%2C%20but%20nothing%20quite%20brought%20Skype%20back%20to%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20video%20calling%20industry.%20Competitors%20ramped%20up%20their%20offerings.%20With%20Microsoft's%20focus%20on%20Teams%2C%20Skype's%20importance%20waned.%20It%20wasn't%20as%20smooth%20a%20process%20to%20use%20it%20on%20mobile%20as%20it%20was%20with%20some%20of%20its%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BBy%20consolidating%20our%20efforts%20to%20focus%20on%20Teams%2C%20we%20can%20provide%20the%20best%20possible%20communication%20and%20collaboration%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Microsoft%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20an%20email%20statement%2C%20adding%20that%20Teams%20offers%20several%20of%20the%20same%20features%20as%20Skype%2C%20including%20group%20calls%2C%20messaging%2C%20and%20file%20sharing%2C%20for%20free.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20we%20see%20Skype's%20run%20come%20to%20an%20end%2C%20it's%20far%20from%20a%20failure.%20%26quot%3BThey%20rose%20at%20the%20right%20time.%20They%20sold%20at%20the%20perfect%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Smooke%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20blog%20HackerNoon%2C%20says%20of%20Skype.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20they're%20dying%2C%20it's%20part%20of%20life.%26quot%3B%20He%20remembers%20the%20platform%20fondly%2C%20using%20it%20for%20long-distance%20job%20interviews%20in%20the%202010s%20and%20chatting%20for%20hours%20with%20long-distance%20romantic%20partners.%20Skype%20isn't%20just%20an%20app%20that%20triggers%20those%20sweet%20nostalgic%20feelings%20but%20also%20the%20foundation%20of%20how%20we%20communicate%20so%20frequently%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deaths%20of%20some%20early-2000s%20social%20platforms%20have%20left%20holes%20in%20our%20collective%20internet%20memory.%20Skype%20was%20the%20place%20where%20I%20could%20talk%20to%20friends%20in%20high%20school%20without%20running%20over%20my%20monthly%20minutes%20on%20my%20flip%20phone.%20It%20was%20how%20I%20talked%20to%20my%20college%20boyfriend%20every%20day%20while%20studying%20abroad%20in%20Spain%2C%20creating%20that%20so-close-yet-so-far%20feeling%20that's%20become%20second%20nature%20with%20regular%20video%20calls.%20Now%20it's%20easy%20to%20feel%20that%20from%20any%20traces%20of%20ourselves%20we%20leave%20online.%20Other%20Web%202.0%20defining%20sites%20like%20Myspace%20and%20Omegle%20have%20shuttered%20or%20become%20unrecognizable%3B%20Imgur%20and%20Tumblr%20have%20banned%20porn%20and%20frustrated%20users.%20With%20Skype's%20demise%2C%20it's%20likely%20most%20of%20us%20won't%20lose%20anything.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20free%20video%20calling%20platforms%20now%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20need%20it%20to%20connect%20and%20keep%20up%20with%20people%20we%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20She%20writes%20about%20the%20biggest%20tech%20companies%20and%20trends.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskype-died-microsoft-destroyed-zoom-whatsapp-facetime-videoconferencing-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746432781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68139c2ca466d2b74ab4bc1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskype-died-microsoft-destroyed-zoom-whatsapp-facetime-videoconferencing-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shut%20down%20by%20Microsoft%2C%20the%20beloved%20video%20chat%20app%20is%20leaving%20behind%20a%20very%20different%20world%20than%20the%20one%20it%20gave%20birth%20to.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ahoover%40insider.com%20(Amanda%20Hoover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskype-died-microsoft-destroyed-zoom-whatsapp-